divs: Sighting DetailsOk on one occasion me and my buddy just got done working out and we were both standing outside and hes talkin to me and i had these expensive sunglasses on and i was thinkin to myself if i was to see a ufo it wouldnt be able to hide from me cause there wasnt a cloud in the sky so all of a sudden it was like 2 in the afternoon i spot this object and i knew right off it was a ufo but i didnt want it to be cause i was just thinkin about seein one so i made every excuse for it not to be one so after i thought it was 4 or 5 diff things and i knew it was 150% ufo i ask my buddy what it was and he said a bag blowin in the wind so i told him it was a ufo so he ran and rab his camera and took a picture of it and soon as he did that it took off it went from one spot to the next like 50 to 100 miles away it was amazing so if you wanna hear more get at me thanks
Summary: Me and a friend saw one but i saw a few of them on a few different occasions in my life .I have at least have 4 to 5 diff siteings during my life if ya wanna hear them give me a call be more than happy to share you with them
